@DataRepublican  is one of the bravest people I know. She was doxxed, has received death threats, and has faced bomb scares. Yet she pressed forward, documenting exactly how deep the abyss goes. Read this book to see what we saw inside the federal government—and to find the way to fix it.

Edward Coristine, aka “Big Balls”
November 30th, 2025

